00:36:38,005 --> 00:36:40,565
So the Denalis' mother
made an immortal Child?

408
00:36:40,875 --> 00:36:41,842
CARLISLE: Yes.

409
00:36:42,777 --> 00:36:44,176
And she paid the price.



411
00:37:07,435 --> 00:37:09,835
