00:49:51,798 --> 00:49:53,857
CARLISLE: Vladimir, Stefan,

589
00:49:54,501 --> 00:49:55,934
you're a long way from home.

590
00:49:56,403 --> 00:49:57,961
What are they doing here?

591
00:49:58,105 --> 00:50:00,539
We heard the Volturi
