00:50:27,334 --> 00:50:28,323
VLADIMIR: Aww.

603
00:50:28,668 --> 00:50:30,465
Still hoping they'll listen?

604
00:50:32,539 --> 00:50:34,973
ELEAZAR: When Aro wants someone 
from a coven

605
00:50:35,108 --> 00:50:39,101
